abstract: The Plaza's Grand Ballroom took a kaleidoscopic turn to white and gold last night for the first of the season's Junior Assemblies. It had been white and green Wednesday for the Junior League Debutante Ball, pink and red for Thursday's Gotham Ball. And this evening it will go bronze, yellow and white for the Grosvenor Debutante Ball.
